                                                    Blog 

Features
1. User will be able to create their account
2. based on the account presence they will  be able to create, delete their own posts, can comment on other peoples posts
3. General public will be able to see other peoples post
4. User will have its own profile page

Nice to have 
1. like 
2. followers and followees
3. profile picture 


Technology implementation
1. Create the structure for the database in mongodb
2. Error route handling
3. Use mongoose orm
4. session and cookie based mechanism
5. authentication
6. authorization
7. security concerns